--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 firewall-scripts: /sbin/iptables wrapper script for typical linux host on VPS.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

README ------------------- This file.
attacker-hosts ----------- Hosts or Networks which attack this host.
belogged-hosts ----------- Traffic from/to these hosts are logged.
extroot-hosts ------------ External super users or developers.
firewall-rules ----------- Policies of each internet services.
make-linux-iptables ------ Wrapper script of firewall command.
monitor-hosts ------------ External monitoring hosts, e.g.) ICMP, SNMP.
my-ipv4-address ---------- This host's IPv4 address.
spammer-hosts ------------ Email spammers(SMTP) and comment spammers(HTTP).
trusted-hosts ------------ Your office gateway or network, or hosts in the same subnet.

